{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"40aa53f82a","title":"征询对第一第二第四方面军作战部署的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8803c49668","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":22,"articleId":"40aa53f82a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1afb04a7cc","type":"paragraph","text":"征询对第一第二第四方面军","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"c45b87d94b","type":"paragraph","text":"作战部署的意见“","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"e8fd1a7e97","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月22日）彭：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"4e50337ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"下列各点请在今明两日考虑见复","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"0a35a5c2fa","type":"paragraph","text":"1.据调香宁二马共有步兵二十个团、骑兵八个团。这个数目属实否。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"f2de2dbde1","type":"paragraph","text":"2.黄河结冰期究有三个月，还是两个月。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"49a083b334","type":"paragraph","text":"3.假如以四方面军待机独立攻青海，一方面军独立攻宁夏，而以二方面军位于中央（例如在眠州、静宁、天水地区）钳制敌人，策应两方，估计能达占青宁两地之自的否，主要的是一方面军有独立战胜宁马之把握否，如果缺少把握之点在于攻城方面而不在于野战方面，则用多兵攻城与少用兵攻城是否有重大之区别","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"a89c4144ad","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"d3bab6655b","type":"paragraph","text":"[21二马，指马鸿速、马鸿宾。马鸿透，当时任国民党军西北“汇”总司令部第十五路军总指挥兼新编第七师师长。马鸿宾，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三十五师师长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"5e5d01b8e3","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]州，即甘肃省县。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"0f51485986","type":"paragraph","text":"4.如以二方面军位于陕甘大道附近钳制毛王何，看一四两方面军分攻宁青之第一步作战结果，再定增加与否及向何方增加，距离与时间上来得及否。我觉得如果冰期在两月以上，则增加是来得及的。判断合于事实否","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"8c0ba937e8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"35dc485328","type":"paragraph","text":"二十二日","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"},{"id":"db8edea175","type":"paragraph","text":"11毛，指毛炳文，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三十七军军长。王，指王均，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第三军军长。何，指何柱国，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部骑兵军军长。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a"}],"page":{"id":"7f397cb366","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"40aa53f82a","start":80,"end":81}}}},"__N_SSG":true}